{"tid":299078,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] [招唱]《一哭一笑》原曲:風起了","createTime":"2017-06-26T18:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T06:54:43.000Z","uid":108844,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40307488cb435d11a33e7d31b5099c0f5b3e2dbd","tid":299078,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:58:13.000Z","msg":"細佬第一次放改詞上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想大家比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想睇下會唔會有人想唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n原曲：張敬軒------風起了<br />\n作詞：陳耀森<br />\n作曲：倪力@Chessman<br />\n編曲：Johnny Yim<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n《一哭一笑》<br />\n<br />\n聽著渺渺的呼叫 是你扮作輕挑<br />\n在被單中一擁而笑 踏向窗邊觀賞夕照<br />\n但美夢過後 仍想貪多兩秒<br />\n共你當初那些分秒 在這天依然會挑起我心跳<br />\n<br />\n任你走 於花開過後默然承受<br />\n時日撇下了 任誰在等候<br />\n沒借口 往日被淡忘怎麼追究<br />\n原諒你又再 掠過眼眸<br />\n<br />\n但你一哭一笑 仍泛濫我思潮<br />\n無奈 抱憾過多少<br />\n但你再不需要 視我 多麼重要<br />\n不再為我傻笑 無需要<br />\n再也不緊要<br />\n<br />\n那部戲角色典雅 但結局太虛假<br />\n像你跟她即使合拍 但要我甘心擔起代價<br />\n是我沒氣力 搖出被愛一卦<br />\n看她將風景火化 旁聽的你又惋惜嗎<br />\n<br />\n但你一哭一笑 仍泛濫我思潮<br />\n無奈 抱憾過多少<br />\n但你再不需要 視我 多麼重要<br />\n心繼續流亡了 而背影多麼渺小<br />\n<br />\n若你有天呼叫 仍會為你動搖<br />\n如若 你尚能打擾<br />\n為你強裝歡笑 為你收起合照<br />\n只配為你微笑 這快樂那樣微小<br />\n只配為你做到沒氣力遐想怎安撫心跳<br />\n愛錯得可笑"},{"pid":"b30dae9ca21e7ccf6c0a265c73f0de60b90144ac","tid":299078,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:05:36.000Z","msg":"補充翻少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首詞主要講一個女仔唔小心做咗人地第三者。個男仔選擇返翻去女朋友身邊，但個女仔唔甘心自己好似被犧牲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b5ad76b1c8c7e5067a165e0fb4325072b7d7d9","tid":299078,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:10:52.000Z","msg":"幾啱音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f82e9d607a28fc7e88341f4e7e0934a8b404d7","tid":299078,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾啱音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但會唔會有啲1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247ca6682b3ceb682b9acf0c0ad0444ab3063d0b","tid":299078,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:31:19.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6798fb6af9828dddcaef9cb7ffd13609d2a2135","tid":299078,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:34:14.000Z","msg":"怎麼追&quot;究&quot;<br />\n但你&quot;一&quot;哭一笑<br />\n只配為&quot;你&quot;微笑 這快樂那樣微小<br />\n只配為&quot;你&quot;做到沒氣力遐想怎安撫心跳<br />\n<br />\n聽咗次原曲，就咁睇有4個位拗音但屬可以接受範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n內容就後半有條理過前半，前半可以交代得清楚啲個故事，咁後半嗰個&quot;若你尚能打擾&quot;會再sad啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油填多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406d3fb713c59a0721c79a66419809e475d7aa87","tid":299078,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>怎麼追&quot;究&quot;<br />\n但你&quot;一&quot;哭一笑<br />\n只配為&quot;你&quot;微笑 這快樂那樣微小<br />\n只配為&quot;你&quot;做到沒氣力遐想怎安撫心跳<br />\n<br />\n聽咗次原曲，就咁睇有4個位拗音但屬可以接受範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n內容就後半有條理過前半，前半可以交代得清楚啲個故事，咁後半嗰個&quot;若你尚能打擾&quot;會再sad啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油填多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺前半有啲含糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid